version_description:
With this update, we've improved some key features for a better overall user experience!

     Create your gift registry within seconds! Just scan items and add them to your registry. 

     Introducing a unified shopping bag experience! Now you can add items while on your desktop or tablet device with the ability to view them on your mobile app.

     Experience improved images, alerts and informational messages on devices like the iPhone 6+, Nexus 6 and more.

     Bug fixes to help improve overall function.

We’ve updated a few key features to improve your experience!

Sharing is caring: Now you can share your loyalty rewards with your friends. 
So many ways to get rewarded: Refer a friend to sign up for our loyalty program and start following Kohl’s on our social channels–you’ll reap the benefits!
It's easier to enter promo codes for discounts (what's not to love?)
Kohl's Gift Cards, now in your Wallet! You can save Gift Cards directly to your Wallet, scan or enter them at checkout, and check balances anytime! 
Bug fixes to improve overall function.

Apple Pay and Visa Checkout — save your information and breeze through checkout

Store Tools — shop and explore your Kohl's store, scan products and apply offers

App Enhancements — improved App performance makes it easier for you to shop

Free Shipping - for orders placed via the Kohl's App while in store

Your Price - lets you see your discounts before checkout

Apple Pay — link your Kohl's Charge for easy checkout, an industry first for retail charge cards (iOS only)

App Enhancements - make it easier for you to shop

Free Shipping - for orders placed via the Kohl's App while in store

Your Price - lets you see your discounts before checkout

Apple Pay — link your Kohl's Charge for easy checkout, an industry first for retail charge cards (iOS only)

App Enhancements - make it easier for you to shop

Never miss another sales event:
Subscribe and receive sales alerts while editing your profile, or when checking out.
Minor bug fixes and performance upgrades.

Spring is here & it's time to freshen up our app with updates that help make your experience easier & more secure.

Here are some of the updates:
-​ ​We've brought over the Q&A feature to our app. Now you can ask, or answer, any question about any product.
Browse our Q&As—chances are, your question's already been answered.
You can also lend a hand to your fellow Kohl's shoppers by answering their questions.
-​ ​Put away your phone charger, because less battery usage means more juice to shop the app.
-​ ​We've made Visual Navigation enhancements that make using the app even easier.
-​ ​We've made some bug fixes and stability improvements, along with additional security enhancements.

You’ll notice a little red badge on our app icon on the home screen. The number on the badge lets you know how many items are stored in your Wallet.
Use your voice to search for items.
General bug fixes & added stability improvements.
General bug fixes & added stability improvements.

Now you can filter your search by your preferred Kohl’s store. Like what you found? Buy it on the App, then pick up it up that same day.
We’ve made your personal store associate, Store Tools, smarter and more precise.
​General bug fixes and performance upgrades
We no longer support iOS 7.0 and below​.

We’ve made it even easier for you to stop paying for shipping when you shop the app and pickup at Kohl’s:
We’ll send you a text message so you’ll know when your order is ready for pickup at Kohl's.
Need to cancel an order? Go ahead and do it directly from the app. (That means, no more having to call customer service!)

There’s so much good stuff to share, so let’s get right to it!

1. Introducing (drum-roll)...Kohl’s Pay, our new in-store payment feature. Link your Kohl’s Charge card to the Kohl’s App and you’ll be able to pay and automatically redeem offers, Kohl’s Cash® and your Yes2You Rewards® directly from your Wallet. It’s as simple as snapping a pic.

2. Never worry about losing your Kohl’s Cash! From now on we‘ll directly deposit your Kohl’s Cash into your Wallet after checkout.

3. Now you can apply Kohl’s Cash and offers to your shopping bag on Kohls.com and then see the same exact bag (Kohl’s Cash, offers and all) from the app. Your bag stays the same no matter where you check out.

4. Notifications always give you the scoop, but now they can also take you where you need to go. All you have to do is swipe right on a notification. If your notification settings are turned off, you’re really missing out. Make sure to turn them on so you’re also in the loop. 

5. We can’t read your mind, but we can make your product search faster by providing possible results as you type.

6. We see our app as a well-oiled, high-powered shopping machine, so we made some general bug fixes and added stability improvements.
General bug fixes. Added stability improvements.

View your Kohl’s Charge balance, available credit and bill due date all from the app. Check it out under My Kohl’s Charge in the app menu.
No need for a price checker when you have the app. Use the scanner feature located at the upper right corner of the app home page.
We’ve added quick links to get you where you need to go, faster and easier. From the top of our home page you can now quickly access Today's Deals, Wallet, Kohl’s Pay (if you’re in store) and your Kohl’s Charge (if you’re not in a store).
And in other news: general bug fixes and performance upgrades.
General bug fixes and added stability improvements.

You probably have a favorite Kohl’s store. Now you can shop that store straight from the App. 
You probably also hate paying for shipping, right? Now you can shop your favorite store from the App and and have your goods ready for pickup (for free) in that same store.
Just let us know which store is your favorite by tapping on “SHOP MY STORE” on the App homepage. We’ll take care of the rest.
Oh yeah, almost forgot: general bug fixes and performance upgrades.
For Apple Watch users:
- Use maps to locate a store near you.

- Pay with your fingerprint when using Kohl’s Pay. Just be sure to enable Touch ID in My Account.
- Now you can update your Kohl’s Pay-linked charge card from the app.
- We’re tuning up the Kohl’s App. It’ll run smoother, faster and smarter.
General bug fixes and performance upgrades.

- Want a quick and easy way to checkout? Try using Masterpass. 
- We’re tuning up the Kohl’s App. It’ll run smoother, faster and smarter.

- We’ve improved the app’s battery usage so you don’t just save on cash, but on battery juice, too.
- Kohl’s Pay users will notice an enhanced offers screen. 
- We’re always tuning up the Kohl’s App so it'll run smoother, faster and smarter.

- You’ll notice we’ve given our product display screens a little makeover. 
- Push notifications are more helpful with richer content. Make sure to opt in to get the most out of the app. Never miss a sale and never let your Kohl’s Cash and Yes2You Rewards expire. 
- General bug fixes and performance improvements.
Fixed minor bugs.

We’re always working to make your Kohl’s experience more convenient, easier and, honestly, just better. 
 - Customer reviews have a new elevated spot on our pages, making them easier to find, access and share.
 - You’ll notice a new and improved search bar that’s more visible and easier to use. 
 - We’ve outfitted our app with a new credit card scanner that automatically loads your credit card number. That means no more having to manually type in your card number. 
 - Kohl’s Cash, Yes2You Rewards and/or offers embedded in emails can now be saved directly to your Wallet without having to sign in. 
 - We’re swatting pesky bugs, making this app run smoother, better.
"We’re swatting pesky bugs, making this app run smoother, better."

It's a snap! Now, if you have a Kohl's Charge, you can use the App to scan a product QR code in our catalogs to make an instant purchase.
Good news if you want to save—set your favorite store or turn location services on and free store pickup will be auto selected for you.
We're constantly working on making the App run faster—and now it performs better than ever with less battery drain. More shopping and less recharging? Not a bad combo.

We've made your checkout experience smoother by refining our offer detection. It's all just a bit smarter.
Now you can take advantage of those excellent rebate offers in the app.
You may notice that many of the great prices you see in our stores are now reflected in the app. It's just another way we're bringing more value to you on the go.
We also zapped more of those pesky bugs.
